Sentencas: Solid oxide fuel cell (SOFC) has been widely recognized as one of the most promising fuel cells.
Titulo: Parameter identification for solid oxide fuel cells using cooperative barebone particle swarm optimization with hybrid learning

Sentencas: The SOFC performance is highly influenced by several parameters associated with the internal multi-physicochemical processes.
Titulo: Parameter identification for solid oxide fuel cells using cooperative barebone particle swarm optimization with hybrid learning

Sentencas: In this work, the optimal modeling strategy is designed to determine the parameters of SOFC using a simple and efficient barebone particle swarm optimization (BPSO) algorithm.
Titulo: Parameter identification for solid oxide fuel cells using cooperative barebone particle swarm optimization with hybrid learning

Sentencas: The cooperative coevolution strategy is applied to divide the output voltage function into four subfunctions based on the interdependence among variables.
Titulo: Parameter identification for solid oxide fuel cells using cooperative barebone particle swarm optimization with hybrid learning

Sentencas: To the nonlinear characteristic of SOFC model, a hybrid learning strategy is proposed for BPSO to ensure a good balance between exploration and exploitation.
Titulo: Parameter identification for solid oxide fuel cells using cooperative barebone particle swarm optimization with hybrid learning

Sentencas: The experimental results illustrate the effectiveness of the proposed algorithm.
Titulo: Parameter identification for solid oxide fuel cells using cooperative barebone particle swarm optimization with hybrid learning

Sentencas: The comparisons also indicate that cooperative coevolution strategy and hybrid learning improve the performance of original PSO algorithm, offering better approximation effect and stronger robustness.
